  "text": "Feelings of defeat were assessed using the Defeat Scale [CITATION_1] . This is a 16 item self-report measure of perceived failed struggle and loss of rank (e.g. 'I feel defeated by life'). Respondents indicate on a five point Likert-type scale the extent to which each item describes their feelings (0=not at all to 4=extremely). This scale has been found to have good psychometric properties [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] ). Cronbach's alpha for the current study was .95.",
